OL,3,CChancellor will change fiscal rules
OL,4,Cfor more investment but won't rule out
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FThe Chancellor told ITV News she is
OL,8,Fnot taking a gamble with the economy
OL,9,Fby changing government financial rules
OL,10,Fto allow more borrowing, as ITV News
OL,11,FBusiness and Economics Editor Joel
OL,12,FHills reports
OL,14,FThe Chancellor has confirmed that she
OL,15,Fwill be making changes to current
OL,16,Ffiscal rules in order to boost
OL,17,Finvestment, but has refused to rule
OL,18,Fout spending cuts.
