OL,3,CChancellor will change fiscal rules
OL,4,Cfor more investment but won't rule out
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FRachel Reeves said that in the Budget
OL,8,Fnext week she would set out two fiscal
OL,9,Frules that the government will stick
OL,10,Fto. The first will be "the most
OL,11,Fbinding, and that is, that we'll pay
OL,12,Ffor day to day spending through tax
OL,13,Freceipts".
OL,15,F"I can confirm today our second rule,
OL,16,Four investment rule, will change the
OL,17,Fway we measure government debt so we
OL,18,Ftake into account assets not just the
OL,19,Fcosts of investment," Reeves said on
OL,20,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
