OL,7,F"That is really important to do what
OL,8,Fthe IMF has said governments should be
OL,9,Fdoing," she added, referring to recent
OL,10,Fwarnings by the International Monetary
OL,11,FFund (IMF) that the UK government's
OL,12,Ffinances cannot be sustained without
OL,13,Feither cuts to the scope of the
OL,14,Fwelfare state or increases in taxes.
OL,16,FWhat are the fiscal rules?
OL,18,FFiscal rules are restrictions on
OL,19,Ffiscal policy set by the government to
OL,20,Fprovide a framework for its own
OL,21,Fdecisions on spending and taxes.
