OL,3,CChancellor will change fiscal rules
OL,4,Cfor more investment but won't rule out
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FThe government currently has three
OL,8,Fmain fiscal rules:
OL,10,FHaving committed to take action in
OL,11,Fline with the IMF's recommendations,
OL,12,FReeves refused to rule out spending
OL,13,Fcuts to some departments.
OL,15,F"I'll set out the detail in the
OL,16,Fspending settlements for next year in
OL,17,Fthe Budget next week. There won't be a
OL,18,Freturn to austerity, but there will be
OL,19,Fdifficult choices," she said.
