OL,7,F"The specific changes, the specific
OL,8,Fpromises that we made in our manifesto
OL,9,Fwere not to increase those taxes on
OL,10,Fworking people, specifically income
OL,11,Ftax, National Insurance and VAT. And
OL,12,Fwe'll stick by those promises in the
OL,13,Fbudget," she said.
OL,15,FYou can watch ITV News' special Budget
OL,16,FDay coverage on October 30 on ITV1 and
OL,17,FITVX.
